Introduction

Sample overview

  • A total of 72 features with 125 metabolites were putatively annotated by MetDNA2, covering 3 different confidence levels.

3. Recursive annotation

  • A total of 157 feature with 309 annotations were obtained via 11 recursive steps.
  • 23 KEGG metabolite used as seed metabolites
  • 134 known metabolites (level 3.1)
  • 152 curated unknown metabolites (level 3.2)
